Call method :
writing a function  inside a class is called method.
Method statement :- Declartinon ,Defination, call
Declartion ,defination should be outside main class
calling should be inside main class inside main method 

Syntax:
function type function name (parameter){
derclation ,defination}
above should be inside main class and main method 
function name(argunments) calling it should be inside main class and main method.

function type :
except void for remaining types we have to return the data.for void we have to print the data
